## EDA Summary — Key Insights

```
1. Quality     → mostly 5 & 6, imbalanced
2. Alcohol     → higher alcohol = better quality ✅
3. Volatile    → higher acidity = worse quality ❌
   Acidity
4. Sulphates   → more sulphates = better quality ✅
5. Residual    → heavily skewed, needs log transform
   Sugar
6. Chlorides   → many outliers, needs treatment
7. Density &   → highly correlated with each other
   Fixed Acidity  (multicollinearity!)
```

